{
  "stem": "23942.8",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And as the taxi pulled near the house where I was supposed to meet my uncle-- the one who I didn't see all the war years and who was my-- you know, my mother's brother, I expected two uncles to meet me.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Instead, I found that one just died before I came as a result of this terrible war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He survived the concentration camp, and he got sick, very sick with typhus, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he just died.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my uncle buried him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I have the picture of the grave and everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he-- only one uncle came, the younger one, came to meet me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But what happened was as the taxi pulled in front of the house, the men just went into the house.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was supposed to meet him at a certain number inside the house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But when I saw him walk in the house, I recognized from the back after not seeing him for years.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I started to scream at the taxi, that's my uncle!",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That's my uncle!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I-- from the back, I recognized him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I ran after him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And by the time he went in the house, he disappeared into the elevator, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I didn't know which door he went in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I forgot the number.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Anyway, I found him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the reunion was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Because, you see, my uncle I did remember before the war-- in the war and before the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And this was the only relative that was remained from my mother's family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he was so happy to see me that-- I don't know, he showed more emotion maybe than my father.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He was such-- it was unbelievable the emotion that I felt when I saw this uncle.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
